/build
/debug
/release
*.aar
*.jar

# ...but libbox.aar IS part of the source drop. It is the sing-box engine (VLESS + AmneziaWG)
# built with gomobile from a toolchain that lives outside this repo, so it cannot be regenerated
# from a fresh clone — without it the project does not build at all. The blanket *.aar rule above
# is inherited from upstream ByeDPIAndroid, which never vendored an .aar.
!/libs/libbox.aar
